server/
 ├── config/
 │    └── db.js              
 ├── controllers/
 │    └── authController.js  
 ├── middleware/
 │    └── authMiddleware.js  
 ├── models/
 │    └── User.js            
 ├── routes/
 │    └── authRoutes.js      
 ├── .env                    
 └── server.js               


Api Base URL
http://localhost:5000/api/auth


| Action        | Method | Endpoint             | Description                    |
| ------------- | ------ | -------------------- | ------------------------------ |
| Register User | POST   | `/api/auth/register` | Creates a new user             |
| Login User    | POST   | `/api/auth/login`    | Authenticates & returns JWT    |
| Get Profile   | GET    | `/api/auth/profile`  | Returns logged-in user profile |

